  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242076.htm", 
  "description": "<p> <strong>不久前一位自称是“Xbox&#160;项目工程师”的网友在国外社区&#160;Pastebin&#160;上发言，表达了自己对于&#160;Xbox&#160;One&#160;各项限制政策被取消的看法。</strong>这位网友表示，微软最终做出这样的决定令他感到非常失望，但这也是没有办法的事情。“如果我们肯花更多时间在向消费者们解释&#160;Xbox&#160;One&#160;政策将带来 的好处上，而不是自己反复折腾，相信玩家最终会认同我们的。当然，出现这样的结局只能怪自己，因为我们无法让玩家们对系统抱有信心。”他说。 </p> <p> <br /> </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2da08ccf/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242076.htm&amp;t=Xbox+One%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%A9%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%9A%BE%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242076.htm&amp;t=Xbox+One%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%A9%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%9A%BE%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242076.htm&amp;t=Xbox+One%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%A9%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%9A%BE%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242076.htm&amp;t=Xbox+One%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%A9%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E9%9A%BE%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242076.htm&amp;